  "title": "Project supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>Since 1981, DAN IMPACT PTE LTD has been providing general contracting and renovation services to commercial business spaces.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will engage directly with clients to define project requirements and scope, prepare and submit detailed quotations, and manage projects through site supervision to ensure timely handover and client satisfaction.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Collaborate with clients to capture and document detailed project requirements and scope of work, ensuring alignment with business objectives</li><li>Develop and prepare accurate, client-tailored project quotations to support successful project acquisition</li><li>Monitor project progress and proactively follow up with stakeholders to secure project awards and maintain momentum</li><li>Lead site supervision and manage project execution to deliver projects on time and meet quality standards</li><li>Implement effective receivables management processes to ensure timely collection of project payments and maintain cash flow</li><li>Adapt work schedule to include after-hours, weekends, and public holidays as needed to meet project deadlines and client expectations</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum two years of experience in the general contracting sector, construction, or related industry</li></ul>",
